### 3. Incomplete Route Protection (`packages/web/src/middleware.ts`)

```typescript
// ❌ Current: Only protects /dashboard
const isProtectedRoute = createRouteMatcher(['/dashboard']);
```

**Fix:** Protect all sensitive routes, including API routes:

```typescript
// ✅ Fixed
const isProtectedRoute = createRouteMatcher([
  '/dashboard(.*)',
  '/api/dashboard(.*)',
  '/api/user(.*)',
  '/settings(.*)',
]);
```

