## 🟡 Medium Issues

### 4. Regex-Based Scanner Risks (`packages/cli/src/agents/scanners/auth.ts`)

If scanning untrusted input, complex regex patterns can cause **ReDoS** (Regular Expression Denial of Service).

**Fix:** Add timeouts and file size limits:

```typescript
// ✅ Add safeguards before scanning
const MAX_FILE_SIZE = 1024 * 1024; // 1MB limit

function scanFile(filePath: string, content: string) {
  if (content.length > MAX_FILE_SIZE) {
    console.warn(`Skipping ${filePath}: file too large`);
    return [];
  }
  // ... existing regex scanning
}
```

